com.percussion.server
Interface IPSCgiVariables

public interface IPSCgiVariables

The IPSCgiVariables inteface is provided as a convenient mechanism for accessing the names of the pre-defined CGI variables.

Since:
1.0
Version:
1.0
Author:
Tas Giakouminakis
